data.description:
BEAUTIFUL TOWNHOME FOR RENT IN THE GATED COMMUNITY OF RIVERWALK RANCH HIGH NOON. THIS TOWNHOME IS A 2 BEDROOM WITH EACH ROOM FEATURING ITS OWN BATHROOM. THE PRIMARY BEDROOM DOES FEATURE A BALCONY. WITH A OPEN FLOORPLAN ON THE 1ST LEVEL THAT HAS A KITCHEN WITH PLENTY OF CABINETS AND STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES. THE FAMILY ROOM FEATURES A GAS FIREPLACE AND CONNECTS TO THE PRIVATE BACKYARD WITH A PATIO. THIS GATED COMMUNITY FEATURES A POOL AND A PARK WITH OTHER SMALLER PARKS THROUGHOUT THE COMMUNITY. CLOSE PROXIMITY TO SHOPPING, RESTAURANTS, GYM AND EASY FREEWAY ACCESS. TENANT PAYS FOR ELECTRICITY AND GAS. WATER-SEWER-TRASH IS INCLUDED AS PART OF THE RENT PER MONTH.

BEFORE SHOWING PROPERTY OWNER REQUEST A TENANT APPLICATION TO BE FILLED OUT ON ZILLOW. NO SMOKING ALLOWED. RENTER IS RESPONSIBLE FOR UTILITIES.
